  "title": "Without Ore",
  "description": "We removed the ore textures to make the game more interesting",
  "body": "<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Is it possible to pass Minecraft without seeing the ore?</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">I think it's possible!&nbsp;<br /></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This resource pack will change the textures of ores to stone! This will add hardcore to the game!&nbsp;<br />With it, you can try your luck, as well as troll your friends by installing it on the server!&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br /><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Screenshots:</span><br /></strong></span></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/396/352/skrinshot-22-09-2021-162421.png\" /><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/396/353/skrinshot-22-09-2021-162432.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><del><strong>Official video:</strong></del></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>More videos:</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;Russian: by \"<a class=\"yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string\" dir=\"auto\" spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/PhantomWay\">Phantom Way</a>\"</span><br /><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EF0d4GbEBwg?wmode=transparent\" height=\"358\" width=\"638\"></iframe></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
